# Shared package

- Export types from `types.ts`; constants from `constants.ts`
- Card data: `src/data/cards.json` — valid JSON, archetype + effects schema
- Pure helpers: `utils.ts` (`canPay`, `describeCardEffectBullets`, clamps)
- No React, no browser APIs, no engine imports

## Card JSON

- `type` in JSON is often archetype (`propaganda`, `economy`); engine infers `asset` | `event`
- `effects` → normalized to `immediateEffects`
- Document new fields in `GAME_MECHANICS.md`

## Breaking changes

Changing `GameState` shape requires coordinated updates in `game-engine` and `apps/web/state`.
